Package com.flipkart.bean

Class Bookings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flipkart.bean.Bookings
  • public class Bookings
extends java.lang.Object
    The Bookings class represents a booking made by a user. It contains information such as booking ID, user ID, creation timestamp, booking status, date, time, slot ID, gym ID, and status.
